VARIABLES
=========
# note: if you dont put in the default value for the provider resource, it will ask at the time of planning or applying the terraform code.
### there are multiple of Data Types:
List of Data Types:
String
number
bool
list()
map() 

Validation Block 
----------------
whenever we want to pass a value for the variable on a condition, we can use a validation block for it. 
e.g


MULTIPLE WAYS TO PASS THE VALUES:
---------------------------------
INPUTTING VARIABLE THROUGH CLI: 

SYSTEM ENVIRONMENT:

THROUGH FILE:

AUTO-SUPPLY INPUTS VIA FILE:



